1.00	Lekin	Lekin...	Lekin (English: But..) is a Hindi drama film made in 1991, loosely based on a short story by Rabindranath Tagore, and directed by Hindi lyricist Gulzar. It stars Vinod Khanna, Dimple Kapadia, Amjad Khan, Alok Nath, and Beena Banerjee, and featured a special appearance by Hema Malini.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/1/12/Lekin.jpg
